high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove to your right.
Grab the pot on the stove.
Carrying the pot, turn around and walk straight to the fridge.
Chill the pot inside the fridge then take it out.
Turn around and walk straight to the stove with the cold pot.
Place the pot to the back of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold pot on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and walk almost to the counter and then turn right and walk to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the front right burner.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Walk back to the stove.
Put the pot on the back right burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pot on the burner.

high_descs: turn around, walk to the stove
grab the pot in the rear right
turn around, walk to the refrigerator
put the pot in the refrigerator for a while, take the pot out
turn around, walk to the stove
put the pot on the rear right stove
anns.task_desc: cool the pot in the refrigerator, put the pot on the stove

high_descs: Turn around and walk until you are even with the stove to your right then turn right and walk to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the bottom right burner of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge so you are facing the front of it.
Put the pot on the bottom shelf of the fridge to the left of the white bowel and let it chill for a while before taking it back out and closing the door.
Turn around and go back to the stove.
Put the chilled pot on the top right burner.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on the stove top.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the stove in the kitchen
Pick up the right most pot from the stove
Turn around and walk up to the fridge
Put the pot into the fridge then remove it
Turn around and walk back to the stove
Put the pot down on the back right stove burner
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled pot on the stove

high_descs: Turn around and right to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the right side.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Put the pot in the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment, and then take the pot out.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Put the pot on the back right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on a stove.
